{"tid":341943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美極]胖夫妻搣走89公斤 婚後10年再行禮影過輯","createTime":"2017-07-31T08:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T18:24:57.000Z","uid":75969,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa20a67dd7cb0fbde17c658eab13221a6bdd4d05","tid":341943,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170731/large/1501470470_5442.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170731%2Flarge%2F1501470470_5442.jpg&h=b76cac8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭法夫（Fife）一對夫婦結婚10年後，決定重新立下誓言，因為兩人都成功減肥，大減了共89公斤後判若兩人，重看當年的婚照自覺「慘不忍睹」，決定重新行禮再拍婚照。<br />\n<br />\n36歲羅伯遜（William Robertson）和34歲賈尼絲（Janice）年輕時缺乏運動又常吃快餐，雙雙有癡肥問題。羅伯遜及後發現患上糖尿病，於是改變生活方式和減肥，「我們都知道自己超重，但我們相愛所以不在乎&hellip;&hellip;我們是好友，一向形影不離，我們決定一同減肥，因為會有競爭所以是件好事。」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩人均成功減了40多公斤</span>，他們重看當年的婚照覺得慘不忍睹，決定再次結婚並重留美好回憶。他們第一次是在註冊處結婚，第二次就在賈尼絲媽媽的家舉行，一眾親友和3名孩子都在場見證。<br />\n賈尼絲又指，<span style=\"color: red;\">第一次結婚時因身形問題難覓嫁衣</span>，但「再婚」時發現減肥後的選擇很多，「當我看到自己(穿上婚紗)，我感動得流淚，羅伯遜看來亦像是另一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170731/large/1501470473_c531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170731%2Flarge%2F1501470473_c531.jpg&h=9f81d636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170731/large/1501470476_ce28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170731%2Flarge%2F1501470476_ce28.jpg&h=338eec05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170731/57019961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170731%2F57019961&d=yX%2F66xiNI6rdAY%2FZDkS4L5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2e66b968\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170731%2F57019961&h=bbb42997\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170731/57019961</a>"},{"pid":"e255f45a5e97478f4b27e01513df50eca05d19be","tid":341943,"uid":33907,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"兩個都靚左好多"},{"pid":"a54811640e44020e22ee824a9b0a7b67facc6c0b","tid":341943,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":77,"score":-75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03362fd5a4f1bab9ec740624091042c09744a694","tid":341943,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:22:40.000Z","msg":"西利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d96a8c5b79a39f60ccc89f383b7bd1f90a6796b","tid":341943,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"條女個手臂同我大脾"},{"pid":"eb698a23bbe4183703639030cce7574245e0e710","tid":341943,"uid":103668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"靚仔靚女左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712645f0a943e76ed9dd6bf1fc45c1c2c4e5e5fb","tid":341943,"uid":34343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>使咩減啫，肥得健康咪得囉</blockquote><br />\n跪求肥得健康教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6529c38b0d195b7f2f2b5b70ba0ec9fe08e096","tid":341943,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:38:27.000Z","msg":"好彩兩個一齊減到<br />\n是但一個減唔到都離硬婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448e62af17e570f34a396105a6d5410b69727265","tid":341943,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit